            			  <p style="padding-left: 23pt;text-indent: -17pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;font-size:12px;">ACCEPTANCE:   Seller’s written acknowledgement and acceptance must be returned properly executed within 3 days from the date of this purchase order (the “Order”). Shipment against this Order without formal acceptance constitutes acceptance of all terms and conditions stated herein.</p>
