            			  <p style="padding-left: 23pt;text-indent: -17pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: justify;font-size:12px;">BILLING/SHIPPING: Seller agrees: (a) to abide by the Buyer’s shipping instructions and, unless otherwise specifically stated, utilize the least expensive (but commercially reasonable) manner of shipment.  Seller shall provide Buyer with a bill of lading and invoice for such shipment;  (b) that the cash discount qualification term, if any, shall be calculated from the later of the date of invoice or the date on which the Goods are received by Buyer;  and</p>
