            			<li style="font-size:12px;" data-list-text="15.">
                    <p style="padding-left: 23pt;text-indent: -17pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: justify;font-size:12px;">Where duty drawbacks are applicable on Goods exported by the Buyer in connection with this Order, the Seller will make any necessary data available to the Buyer for such claim.</p>			
                  </li>
            			<li style="font-size:12px;" data-list-text="16.">
            			  <p style="padding-left: 23pt;text-indent: -17pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;font-size:12px;">The parties agree, whether expressly, freely and spontaneously, that any claim or demand arising out of this contract shall be resolved in the first instance, necessarily, by the Center for Conciliation and Arbitration of the Chamber of Commerce of Costa Rica .</p>
